        Vendor Finance in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        It is uncommon. It carries real risk for sellers. And in the right circumstances, it can unlock a sale that otherwise would not happen. Here is what you need to understand before considering it.
      </p>
